 TIME NOT POSTING SOMETHING ON MY FEED. EASY, I&#39;M BACK ðŸ˜„ðŸ˜„ðŸ˜„ May I tell you a story? I was kinda sad earlier today knowing that there are people wrote a book review and critisized the physical appearance of its writer at the same time (explained it a lil bit on my Stories). You know, the anonymous included body-shaming things in their review and I was like&#8230; what&#39;s the freakin&#39; relation, dude? Of course people have their own rights to make a review based on their knowledge, experience, or taste, but when it comes to someone&#39;s appearance, it&#39;s none of their business. Not yours as well. What I wanna tell you is&#8230; dear writers and readers, let&#39;s support each other. Writers need readers and vice versa. Write an honest review in a polite way, don&#39;t hurt others. Also, always stay positive! Have a wonderful weekend, bookworms! ðŸ˜Šâ¤ &#8211; &#8211; &#8211; &#8211; &#8211; &#8211; #bookstagramfeature #bookmail #bookphotography #bookstafeatures #bookish_indonesia #bookofthemonth #yalovin #bookishfeatures #met_createchange #epicreads #bookflatlay #culturetripbooks #booknerdigans #igreads #bookstagram #booksaddict #totalbooknerd #featuremybooks #whatimreading #libraryofbookstagram #bookworm #becauseofreading #TheBookstagram #bibliophile #vscobooks #bookish #booknookstagram #bookfeaturepage #bookblogger #booktographyid</a></p><p style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;">A post shared by <a href="https://www.instagram.com/sintiawithbooks/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px;" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow"> Sintia Astarina</a> (@sintiawithbooks) on <time style=" font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px;" datetime="2018-08-04T11:52:06+00:00">Aug 4, 2018 at 4:52am PDT</time></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></div><p>Karena banyak yang protes dengan algoritma Instagram belakangan ini, ternyata para user punya cara lain untuk mengakalinya, yaitu dengan mengoptimalkan penggunaan Inta Stories. Apalagi, fitur ini bakal bikin konten yang dihasilkan jadi lebih bervariasi. Selain bisa menambah tulisan, <em>emoticon</em>, atau stiker, kamu juga bisa menyertakan jam, lokasi, <i>hashtag, poll,</i> juga animasi GIF. Jadi, pas Bookstagrammer lain melihat Insta Stories-mu, mereka juga akan menikmatinya.</p><p style="padding-left: 30px;"><b>Baca juga: </b><b><a href="https://www.sintiaastarina.com/big-bad-wolf/" rel="bookmark">Pengalaman Borong Buku di Big Bad Wolf Jakarta (Bonus: 5 Tips Biar Enggak Kalap)</a></b></p><p>Oh ya, ada tips tambahan, nih. Coba deh, kamu bikin atau ngelakuin SFS alias Shoutout for Shoutout. Jadi, kamu meng-<i>capture feed</i> orang lain dan mengunggahnya ke Insta Stories kamu dengan tujuan untuk mempromosikan akun tersebut. Biasanya, akun yang kamu promosikan akan mempromosikan balik akun kamu di Insta Story mereka. Jadi, istilahnya, kalian bisa saling tukar <i>followers.</i></p><h4><b>6. Adakan Book Giveaway</b></h4><div class="sbi-embed-wrap"><blockquote class="instagram-media sbi-embed" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/BjUvlMBl3eY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="12" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BjUvlMBl3eY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" background:#FFFFFF; line-height:0; padding:0 0; text-al